data.description:
Charming 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Home on 7+ acres.  Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this inviting residence.  Featuring an open floor plan, the home boasts a specious layout with split bedrooms for added privacy.  Indulge in culinary delights within the well-appointed Kitchen, seamlessly flowing in the Dining room and Family Room.  Brick Fireplace with Gas Logs.  Enjoy the serenity of nature on the front porch or the screened porch, and soak up the sunshine on the expansive deck. Flex Space and Finished Bonus room over the garage.
Crawl Space is partially cemented for great storage.
